d4aa516f7b35c2eddd5c534391fd6363429633aea3b4b2e8e46b1fe192986c79f91bf9e3e808992ce524ffc3ac96cc3952d1a1e7c3b355b7f97ffa9badc8b8d0  0001-Work-around-git-commit-s-lack-of-robustness-by-provi.patch"
